{"tid":563992,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"終於可以直接支持Wintergatan...","createTime":"2018-02-17T13:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T00:25:26.000Z","uid":138409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c7316dc1f3a9c7b6399acd263ccbf89f0696305f","tid":563992,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:17:28.000Z","msg":"入正題之前首先有無人聽過／知道Wintergatan呢對band<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果無，容許我吹奏下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有就skip it<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【吹奏開始】<br />\n一直以來都覺得Wintergatan呢支band好正<br />\n<br />\n因為他們的曲風合我口味（類似鋼片琴／音樂盒之類...tranquilizing的音樂風格），<br />\n而且極有創意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（例如以下呢段音樂，將木鋸當小提琴拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2xgWuw3TOJA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2xgWuw3TOJA&d=u16ti%2BQKRfEP63qtE5Xr1Nr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=4a9b2bc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2xgWuw3TOJA</a><br />\n寫完音樂仲要任人免費download，不設paywall<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每次down完都有點過意不去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最勁係明明玩音樂，結果連mechanical engineering都玩埋<br />\n之前整過部Marble Machine<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IvUU8joBb1Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIvUU8joBb1Q&d=u16ti%2BQKRfEP63qtE5Xr1Nr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=b62cdb7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IvUU8joBb1Q</a><br />\n<br />\n現在整緊部升級版- Marble Machine X<br />\n(每個部件的製作過程都公開，而且會在留言區收集意見改良設計，crowdsourcing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLLLYkE3G1HED6rW-bkliHbMroHYFf4ukv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fplaylist%3Flist%3DPLLLYkE3G1HED6rW-bkliHbMroHYFf4ukv&d=u16ti%2BQKRfEP63qtE5Xr1Nr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=dc7f3320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLLLYkE3G1HED6rW-bkliHbMroHYFf4ukv</a><br />\n依家他們的目標是帶著Marble Machine X進行巡迴演出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望會來香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n【吹奏完畢】<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一直以來有follow開他們的channel，最近得知他們用了YouTube的Sponsor功能<br />\n即刻狗衝落樓下7仔增值Google play account<br />\n<br />\n每月捐$25，捐得過啊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以本文重點是<br />\n<br />\n1. 見到外國Youtuber如此犀利，再望望香港哥班，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. Youtuber廣告收入逐漸減少未嘗不是好事，至少單靠clickbait騙流量班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而有能力、質素頂尖哥班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 純粹想推廣Wintergatan，令更多人認識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6075e5be0892734ca2914a509bd710e4d1f2134","tid":563992,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:29:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d7709da0feb2b5d4ec56f67b703a3e05d97edeb4","tid":563992,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:45:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"495208d0182c7be14f902ab55ccc97e4c389d35a","tid":563992,"uid":43231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T13:53:09.000Z","msg":"聽過 除咗marble machine<br />\n仲鐘意sommarfagel<br />